{"tid":2514183,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"湯文亮：移民不賣樓現象","createTime":"2021-05-03T05:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:48:26.000Z","uid":230530,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3a06aa24ca965ec9be47ba8a13c292c343a95c51","tid":2514183,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"上星期中原指數上升1.65%，距離兩年前歷史高位只有3.84%，又不是遙不可及的事，有很多人在英國推出BNO移民計劃之後話香港樓市會大跌，理由是不少香港人賣樓移民。<br />\n<br />\n老實說，的確有人用BNO移民，數字現在暫未能夠確認，但從中小學的退學潮，我相信不是一個小數目。不過，樓價不跌反升，我倒想聽一聽那些話移民賣樓，令樓價下跌的人解釋，原來答案都幾玄，那些人話，移民還移民，賣樓還賣樓，兩者是沒有關連。這個答案我是同意，但點解他們唔早一些講。"},{"pid":"3d22e4e66dfc12a33826b6e42215f36f6b9b2eba","tid":2514183,"uid":93986,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"因為有支那人頂住個市<br />\n但都唔代表要係度生活囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那人喜歡食屎，咁香港人屙屎俾佢地食又有咩所謂。"},{"pid":"ecc6a30e1ecaa01afa3183edbaa5cfe91257bbb4","tid":2514183,"uid":2054,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVZ11crW1oJL5ENs44SEMJBV7RX9YFWsj6xhJAsTBC1Z4?filename=URttzT7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURttzT7.jpg&h=b7aa57a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92fedd1c28f3d5e4d96bcbd74994bbd62dd25533","tid":2514183,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTJQ8cqy6NXoFtzp5DtbYMcY5GHcvc9ZuCbyws4CWqVKM?filename=RqG5SBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqG5SBE.jpg&h=2a457d8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea9ce1fd7831921f2f6e86b41ce19acb0a784cb1","tid":2514183,"uid":1455,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"找數吞file未"},{"pid":"bb0a42a